title: Omaha Steaks CEO: Beef Demand at an All-Time High
description: Nate Rempe, CEO of Omaha Steaks, discusses new dietary guidelines and beef supply and demand with Romaine Bostick and Katie Greifeld on “The Close.” He says beef demand is at an all-time high. (Source: Bloomberg)
